Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura is just Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And she'll always probably\Njust be Shimamura in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.80,0:00:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really get it,\Nbut there's just a peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.34,0:00:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Something that just gets my guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.14,0:00:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shukoh... Shukoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.64,0:00:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so you did show up again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.10,0:00:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And who might this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.90,0:00:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She is {\i1}the {\i0}Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.86,0:00:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that even mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.36,0:00:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oho... So you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So, uh... What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.41,0:00:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike my foolish compatriot,\NI have come prepared with a name!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.04,0:00:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please call me Yashiro Chikama.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come to Earth in search of my compatriot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Compatriot...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Compatriot? Oh, compatriot. Like a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.72,0:02:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, there's more of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather, did you just say "Earth"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My compatriot came to this planet on a mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but they haven't been back ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.32,0:02:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So I had no choice but to search for them,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but it appears that I have landed\Nin the wrong location.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.82,0:02:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Alrighty, Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You go ahead and enjoy talking\Nabout the unknown with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha! I sense some fishies over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.29,0:02:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sneaky, sneaky, sneak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, Hino. So the real reason\Nyou invited me fishing was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So I hear that your name is Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.10,0:03:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear that you're so popular that all\Nthe locals come in droves to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm definitely not that Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, such modesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I have come from the future,\Nso I am not a local.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so we're clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, and I've come from the past.\NNice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be a typical earthling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you take that thing off?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.54,0:03:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My face is not quite ready,\Nso I do ask for your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.59,0:03:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is your face going to be delivered\Nfrom the bread factory or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you be looking for your friend,\Nor rather, your compatriot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this something philosophical?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I have already confirmed\Nthat my compatriot is safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,so I figured I would take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So they contacted you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.86,0:04:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're able to contact each other,\Nyou can probably find each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And there is a reason that we cannot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:15.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,Shukoh... Shukoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Plop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't seem to get a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's important that you realize that first...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't seem to get a bite.\NThings aren't going as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But that basically means\Nthat you've started something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You just felt like doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.86,0:04:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Fishy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Heck yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All we can do from here\Nis wish for a bright future,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and cast our lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yeah... That happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I that boring?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you not say it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I was pretty busy\Nat work yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.02,0:05:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you have a part-time job\Nsomewhere? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you'd probably show up if I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you're working is admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi once said that I was like a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that I keep my distance from others\Nmakes me cat-like, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Though there is a part of me\Nthat doesn't want to open up to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But Adachi's basically the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.40,0:06:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi dozing off with her head on my lap\Ndefinitely reminded me of a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this is better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if I lay down this way,\NI can smell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Wait, do I have bad BO?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.42,0:06:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you lack elegance, Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Elegance... Hm... Elegance, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think anyone's told me that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.19,0:06:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna actually go to class\Nwith me this afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What brought that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, attendance and such...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm saying is, it'd be more fun if we both\Nmade it as second-years together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Together...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.62,0:07:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it wouldn't hurt once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, hey... Let's go somewhere\Nonce classes are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have other plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Not today...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I never really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll actually get a bite today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,School is its very own, unique society,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you brought that outside,\Nit confused things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm sure that some people would just\Nprefer to live out their lives at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.99,0:07:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That aside, I want to catch a bright future.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And for that to happen, I've got to\Ncast my line, or nothing will begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How were your classes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Japanese history was fine, but I definitely\Ndon't understand math anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been to more classes than you and yet,\Nneither makes sense to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,so where does that put me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:08:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You seemed to get a lot of attention, Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm pretty sure you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably because you're so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is the first time\Nanyone's ever called me pretty, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Your boy... friend\Ndoesn't call you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never had one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... I guess everyone must be blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait, where's your bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.51,0:08:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's out for repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... So you actually\Nwalked to school. Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I thought you'd be here, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to classes tomorrow, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:09:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going to at least do my best\Nto go for more than three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say, Miss Adachi?\NWhy don't we put in a little effort together?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess... I can try a little harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Want a bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right back at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi? Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.36,0:09:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, there's some cream.\NThis is what you were waiting for, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should we go after we eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Being with other people\Nseems to bring a little bit of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Not understanding something.\NSomething being a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to mend relationships.\NPutting in effort to find solutions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes a bit of happiness is rolling\Naround in between all that negativity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like when you're a kid and you find\Na tiny ball that you thought you'd lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.19,0:10:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to believe that\Nthe fact that I met Adachi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to bring me a brighter future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's awkward, I'll let go! Like right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't awkward. You just startled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I not then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.74,0:10:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like being coddled, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:05.49,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Pedestrian-Vehicle Separated Signal"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...that surprised...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shukoh... Shukoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shukoh... Shukoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you here, so I thought I would say hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.47,0:11:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You really just walk around\Nin front of the station in that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is my finest outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I smell something exquisitely sweet\Nfrom your fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is quite nice. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably donuts, since I just ate some.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Donuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.33,0:11:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?\NThough I saw that coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:12:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a blip on my radar!\NThere're donuts in there, aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but don't grab at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.01,0:12:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you give me one of those d-donuts,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall reveal one of\Nthe secrets of the universe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? This is for my little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If they eat a donut, they'll take off\Ntheir helmet, and I can see their face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:19.72,On Top,,0,0,0,,Poik.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine. You can have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.37,0:12:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... You can have this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so this is a donut.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Squeak, squeak, squeak, squeak...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Pshuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:44.15,On Top,,0,0,0,,Munchy, munchy, munchy, munchy, munchy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not taking off your helmet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Munchy... Gulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Plop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this was nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:56.08,On Top,,0,0,0,,It's very sweet!\N- It's oh so sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never heard of donuts before?\NWhat kind of dance is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any more sweets?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:12:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Buy some yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.82,0:13:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get my bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, was she mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like me to tell you what just happened
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of one of the universe's secrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.63,0:13:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She's mad because she didn't get a donut!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea if this self-proclaimed person
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.51,0:13:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,from the future is going to\Ngreatly change my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like things usually change your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Because no one knows what the future holds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, relationships are hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, Shimamura thinks\NI'm prettier for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.33,0:14:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But she is greatly mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say that Shimamura is way cuter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Her dreamy eyes, the way\Nshe modestly moves her lips...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My eyes keep looking at her face,\Nespecially her lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a dream where I kissed Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I'm into that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I just want to be closer\Nwith Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's definitely not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no deep meaning behind that kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope! None!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.11,0:15:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying I'd never kiss her...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not saying I absolutely want to, either?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If there was no one else within\Na 5-kilometer radius from Shimamura,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and she was in a deep sleep and an all-knowing\Ndeity just happened to reassure me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that she wasn't going to wake up\Nin the next 24 hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.33,0:15:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe I'd get bored\Nafter 23 hours and I might
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,kiss her once to relieve some boredom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.13,0:15:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm definitely not that.\NI just want Shimamura to put me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.85,0:15:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I want Shimamura to think of me first\Nwhen she hears the word "friend."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that may sound a bit possessive...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,To be quite honest, I've been wondering
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,how much of a friend\NShimamura actually sees me as.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:16:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I just like her other friends?\NOr does she have other feelings for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:03.83,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Sunday"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcom--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you it was embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.11,0:16:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. It suits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see them much anymore at our house\Nsince she entered high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.07,0:16:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oho... Are you two in the same class?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.87,0:16:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just order already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have {\i1}tantanmen{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.13,0:16:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll have...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, Shimamura\Ndoesn't really understand me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.38,0:16:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but I could say the same about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't push me away when I rely on her,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:17:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but she doesn't try to rely on anyone herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.77,0:17:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That was how I saw Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were finally shaping up,\Nand now look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.28,0:17:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Our teacher. They were asking me\Nwhere you were like I'd be able to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.24,0:17:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking about how cute\Nyou looked yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.70,0:17:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? B-But you're cute, too, Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's not like I did anything.\NMaybe I'll go there to eat again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't. Please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kidding. I'm not sure if I want\Nto go again with my family...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It is sort of embarrassing\Nwhen you're with family--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:45.54,On Top,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's Shimamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, so you did come.\NCan I sit next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... You're... Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:17:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Adachi! Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgot her name but somehow\Nreally thought whispering would work?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.04,0:18:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.88,0:18:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rare for you to eat school lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I don't hate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:15.01,On Top,,0,0,0,,Well my dear {\i1}maman {\i0}slept in today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Their noisiness isn't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It reminded me of lunchtime in\Ngrade school and was a bit nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But it also felt like they were cutting\Ninto my time alone with Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't deny that I felt\Nthat this didn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi, what are you going\Nto do about the afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I plan to go to class... I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...could go to your house today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.26,0:19:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Big... Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.23,0:19:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. Oh, this is my friend. From yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.07,0:19:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.03,0:19:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a bit shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So your room's on the first floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can sit wherever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.31,0:19:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.56,0:19:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say it, don't say it, don't say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, do you mind if I sit...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:19:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.99,0:20:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Like... Between your legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.91,0:20:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I just say?!\NOh, my God. I'm a complete weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.74,0:20:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, it's okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, huh? I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a dream? Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura's legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.98,0:20:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.35,0:20:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.06,0:20:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hello?! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.53,0:20:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Well, my little sister likes\Nto sit like this. Isn't this normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's weird. It's super weird! My clavicle hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:49.77,On Top,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:51.27,On Top,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:53.33,On Top,,0,0,0,,Do you have a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually, people feel pain in their chest,\Nbut I'm feeling it in my bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:54.85,On Top,,0,0,0,,Do you think I have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:56.02,On Top,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:21:00.17,On Top,,0,0,0,,You're right. Actually,\NI told you that the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:21:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My bones start grinding so much\Nthat it feels like they're out in the open.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:01.57,On Top,,0,0,0,,Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:03.28,On Top,,0,0,0,,Do you have one, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to relax...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.01,0:21:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.05,0:21:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And I immediately figured out
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.89,0:21:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,how to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.48,0:21:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I like... you, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.73,0:21:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?! What did I just try to say?\NDid I say it? Wait, did I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I think... I like you, Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.45,0:21:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, I'm done for.\NI can't... I'm an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.87,0:21:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... This is... This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I think I like you... Possibly, maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.75,0:21:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, like... really like...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a complete moron...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... You okay? Are you breathing?\NYour face is like bright red...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.49,0:22:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What the efffffff...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.95,0:22:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What the efffffff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.89,0:22:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! Ow, ow... My neck hurts. It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.29,0:22:22.05,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 2: Adachi Question"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.52,0:22:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the sun were to set and rise again,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.06,0:22:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,would tomorrow even come for me?{\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.01,0:24:07.00,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Next Time: 'Isosceles Triangle'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.70,0:23:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Adashimapedia: Aliens!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.70,0:23:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We are aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.99,0:23:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it weird for aliens\Nto call themselves "aliens"?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.37,0:23:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's actually a good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.50,0:24:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They should be more specific, like,\N"We are boobliens. Let us fondle your ti--"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.38,0:24:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to force you aliens outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.29,0:24:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been defeated...
